projects.description:
Power Networking Boot Camp™ is the only training of its kind to go deeper than just overcoming fear of talking to strangers and worn out delivery techniques on networking. With our unique, proven AttentionalNetworking™ system, we drill down to the foundation of your connections – your preparation. You will learn to prepare powerfully focused, crystal clear meeting/events and then connect with others with confidence and power. 

What to expect: 

►The Attentional Networking™ method of attracting new clients, influence and deeply connecting with them. A technique designed for you to hit a home run every time.
►The secrets of effective & authentic connections.
►How to find, capture and develop powerful connections to grow and expand your business.
►The Benefits of Networking [Setting objectives]
►The mind set and the skills set you need to become a real networker;
►The secrets of how the pro networkers source their best contacts, alliances and prospects;
►Little known authentic ways to accelerate conversations and influence outcomes;
►Simple networking – do it your own way!
►Hidden strategies for building relationship that last;
►Sincerity and Authentic Attention™ – an impact and being remembered when networking.
►The importance of follow up and staying in touch;
►Practical tips and tricks in maintaining a professional network.
